# {{.Name}}

Scaffolded by [hex](https://github.com/jordanbrauer/hex).

## Layout

```
{{.Name}}/
├── main.go                       # entry point
├── app/
│   ├── boot.go                   # provider registration order
│   ├── build/                    # build metadata
│   ├── command/                  # cobra command tree (root + subcommands)
│   └── provider/                 # service providers
├── domain/                       # your business logic
├── infrastructure/               # driver adapters (SQL repos, HTTP clients)
├── lib/                          # local utility packages
├── config/                       # embedded TOML configuration
{{- if ne .Dialect "none" }}
├── database/                     # migrations.go + migrations/*.sql
{{- end }}
└── justfile
```

## Running

```bash
go mod tidy
go run .
```

## Generators

Add code with the `hex` CLI (from the project root):

```bash
hex make:provider payments        # app/provider/payments.go, wired into app/boot.go
hex make:domain user              # domain/user/{user,repository,service,errors}.go
hex make:migration create_users   # database/migrations/<ts>_create_users.{up,down}.sql
```

## Build

```bash
just build          # produces bin/{{.BinaryName}} with ldflags-populated version info
just                # list all recipes
```
